From: frerk@tk.telematik.informatik.uni-karlsruhe.de (Frerk Meyer)
Subject: Re: I think my monitor is exploding..help
Date: 27 Sep 1993 08:26:01 GMT

You are lucky. Your Monitor has a self protection feature,
when you are using it outside of the specifications.
After a while it manages to synchronize, but you should not rely on
that. So calculate a standard mode like 640x480x256x60Hz before going
for the ultimate. vgaset may help you (and your Monitor).
